  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FermatGenerator
    Implementation of Fermat's algorithm for primality test.
    HeuristicGenerator
    Tests number's primality by combining Fermat test and Miller-Rabin test, since they give probable primes.

    Test cases for Heuristic Generator.
    MillerRabinGenerator
    Implementation of Miller-Rabin Primality Test algorithm.
    MillerRabinGeneratorTest
    Test cases for Miller-Rabin Generator.
    SegmentedSieveGenerator

    SieveGenerator

    SieveGeneratorTest

    TrialDivisionGenerator
    A classic prime number generation algorithm working in O(n*log(n)).
    TrialDivisionGeneratorTest
    Test cases for Trial & Division Generator.
